Ginger Lewis, Leigh Ann Barton's cousin, said the whole family was aware that Mark Barton was a suspect in the 1993 slaying of his first wife, Debra Barton, and her mother, Eloise Powell Spivey.
(AP) --The investor who killed his family and nine people at two brokerage firms vowed in a note to kill ``the people that greedily sought my destruction,'.
Barton, a chemist and securities day trader, wrote in his letter that he killed his current wife, Leigh Ann, night and his two children, 11-year-old Matthew and 8-year-old Mychelle, night.
